PrecisAppointment of EVELYNE HENRY, of Cumberland, Ontario, as a Deputy Chairperson of the Public Service Staff Relations Board, to hold office during good behaviour for a term of three years, and order that EVELYNE HENRY shall be deemed to be employed in the Public Service for the purposes of the Public Service Superannuation Act, effective July 6, 1998.
